pan></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"634eef6dc4085f45f9923ed4a4e703cabf803578","tid":1497524,"uid":110321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a47cf92b2f9a89b45c6b6d1069d182ce6c249baf","tid":1497524,"uid":290313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"[823人鏈]如果唔夠人，可以拎長遮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497500\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497500</a>"},{"pid":"8c5bd1ab21ddb85cdf02268efabb56c43399812d","tid":1497524,"uid":108337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">搞到全世界經濟</span><br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多<span style=\"color: red;\">受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界陪葬</span>既時候，你覺得啲<span style=\"color: red;\">大國會唔會出聲？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點係揸車/搭車遊覽東涌令交通擠塞，癱瘓機場交通，唔係行入機場入面</strong><br />\n空管主任返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇</span>"},{"pid":"9e73458a4a0dc9b025b6eb27aa6fdc7ba518a477","tid":1497524,"uid":184597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"我唔想做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82356b80c7e31b889f854e1b556bcf6d56d0d59f","tid":1497524,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"人鏈要人"},{"pid":"f7af2fc082865d469697ce95bbc57a7b57480d06","tid":1497524,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個deadline.<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果deadline前政府都唔回應五大訴求, 會行動升級</strong></span> 後果自負<br />\n<br />\n用意: 先小人後君子<br />\n1)迫使政府回應<br />\n2)市民有心理準備當日會有行動<br />\n3)令市民知道當天有行動係源於政府唔回應 <br />\n    (令佢地明白若果政府肯回應就唔會有行動阻礙到佢番工, 出街)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 五大訴求</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況, 解散、追究及重組警隊<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n[下一步棋] 救香港 Set Deadline 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"},{"pid":"986b8adedd9398a1b5a076e196fd35712c420c84","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707415f30569b30f8657db373c23127bddf694e8","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e21807c0693f78284865dd13b39ca8921a8f60e","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba71d1914f2b478c874874a3ad0abfad51b3bacc","tid":1497524,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"寫信向IATA 等國際航空組織投訴中國<br />\n干預航空自由同營運<br />\n危害機組人員及乘客安全<br />\n如果中國再唔收手就作出懲罰<br />\n例如禁止中國航空公司飛歐盟 美國 澳洲 日本等<br />\n睇下邊個快收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外向中美貿易代表/白宮經濟顧問/國際貿易組織etc 投訴中國干預經濟自由<br />\n等美國多d 談判籌碼<br />\n逼中國唔好再搞香港<br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳呢個訊息等多d 人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家copy n paste 等多d 人知道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇埋下面2 條link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496792</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493700</a>"},{"pid":"a8edab8b538a6705ed810fc3eb624ac02c1e039d","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34caa9464adf3a6666309f7521e7d07654eb60eb","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b62892894a80572a7565dec7d4f164786775aa2","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a90c7cb38049bd90791527599c542eec196602","tid":1497524,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":